{"tid":1811100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"CGA又袋旅發局200萬搞除夕抽獎  2019年連登仔：CGA係黃","createTime":"2020-01-04T11:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T13:21:17.000Z","uid":79317,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cadb58ebfe43e8179f921842b737d917a2fe02f7","tid":1811100,"uid":79317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200104/60450613?fbclid=IwAR2G9o1qzd3hADKS2ihqyBAHQc2Lc2wJQr4LyF7vI8Lx3FDbIKIzVp02AC0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F60450613%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2G9o1qzd3hADKS2ihqyBAHQc2Lc2wJQr4LyF7vI8Lx3FDbIKIzVp02AC0&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=958adfaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F60450613%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2G9o1qzd3hADKS2ihqyBAHQc2Lc2wJQr4LyF7vI8Lx3FDbIKIzVp02AC0&h=f9e88927\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200104/60450613?fbclid=IwAR2G9o1qzd3hADKS2ihqyBAHQc2Lc2wJQr4LyF7vI8Lx3FDbIKIzVp02AC0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1GhgOi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1GhgOi.png&h=9f338da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有在旅發局承判商列表內、專營網頁及程式開發的IT人向《蘋果》表示，自己的公司未曾收過相關項目招標訊息，而今晨程鼎一就透露，負責網頁系統公司有舉辦電競及網上抽獎經驗，過程符合內部程序。曾協助旅發局籌辦電競音樂節的電競公司Cyber Games Arena在程鼎一見記者後發聲明，承認為活動網頁系統供應商，就活動引起公眾不便致歉，表示由於準備時間不足，加上程式由測試伺服器搬遷到上線伺服器出現技術問題，以及短時間內的電郵認證超出收發容量限制，引致抽獎活動延誤。<br />\n他又指出，類似項目網頁系統開發成本一般比重較大，有關開支料需140至150萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解旅發局每次都將d野比哂CGA接，但連登仔仲死撐護航佢地係黃<br />\n發完夢有入去換衫個D 好自為知，入面好多CAM仲有會員資料系統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dccf475930c42448fb05c9af791ee1c503f8d5d","tid":1811100,"uid":186,"